### ============================================
### UNIT API TESTING
### ============================================
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### 1. GET ALL UNITS (Default pagination)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/units
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 2. GET UNITS WITH PAGINATION
### Page 0, Size 10
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/units?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 3. SEARCH UNITS BY NAME
### Search for "kg" or "Kilogram"
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/units?search=kg
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 4. FILTER UNITS BY STATUS
### Get only active units
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/units?status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 5. SEARCH + FILTER BY STATUS
### Search "kg" in active units only
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/units?search=kg&status=active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 6. SORT UNITS BY NAME (Ascending)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/units?sortBy=name&sortDir=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 7. SORT UNITS BY CREATED DATE (Descending)
### ============================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/units?sortBy=createdAt&sortDir=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
